beer.beer_description:
This bold Canadian Red Ale is the perfect expression of balance between malt and hops.
Big chewy caramel malt flavours give way to drying bitterness from roasted barley.
Complimented by earthy tones of maple syrup, providing a true celebration of Canada.

Malt: Ale, Double Roasted Crystal, Medium crystal, Roasted Barley
Hops: Columbus
Other: Fenugreek, Maple Syrup
